<div id="pf9d" class="pf w0 h0" data-page-no="9d"><div class="pc pc9d w0 h0"><img class="bi x9 yee w5 h16" alt="" src="bg9d.png"/><div class="t m0 x9 h6 yf ff1b fs4 fc0 sc0 ls9 ws0">156 <span class="ffc fs0 ls0">  <span class="ff1b">中国人民大学问答 </span></span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h7 y18 ff6 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"> </div><div class="t m0 x9 h1 yb4 ff6 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"> </div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y2a ffd fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">了</div><div class="t m0 x74 h17 y1ba ffd fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5</div><div class="t m0 x9e h4 y2a ffd fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">，<span class="_ _15"></span>就像漂浮在河里的人，<span class="_ _15"></span>因怕溺水而最终渴死一样，<span class="_ _15"></span>我们</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y2b ffd fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">听闻佛法若不去修持，对自己则没有任何利益。 </div><div class="t m0 x67 h23 y57 ff15 fs2 fc0 sc0 ls59 ws0">（四） <span class="_ _1b"> </span><span class="ff16 ls0">问<span class="ffc fs3 ls5a">：我读过一些佛经，只是从语言文字层面</span></span></div><div class="t m0 x9 hc y58 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">接触了佛教。请问，应该怎样去实修呢？ </div><div class="t m0 x67 h3 y134 ff16 fs2 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">答<span class="ffd">：<span class="fs3 ls5b">修行分为观察修、安住<span class="ls5c">修。观察修是在日常生活</span></span></span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y135 ffd fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">中，将自己所听到的教理，慢慢去思维、去串习。比如说，</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y136 ffd fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">你明白一切万法无常之后，<span class="_ _8"></span>就可将它贯穿于现实生活中。<span class="_ _8"></span>安</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y14a ffd fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">住修，<span class="_ _5"></span>则是在寂静的环境中，<span class="_ _5"></span>断除一切分别念，<span class="_ _5"></span>然后去观修</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y32 ffd fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">它的法义。<span class="ff6 fs4"> </span></div><div class="t m0 x75 h7 y245 ff6 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"> </div><div class="t m0 x9 h7 yf3 ff6 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">                                        <span class="_ _13"></span>               <span class="_ _8"></span> </div><div class="t m0 x9 h18 yf4 ff6 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5</div><div class="t m0 x6d h1d yf5 ff6 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">  <span class="ff12">《华严经》云：<span class="_ _a"></span>“譬人水所漂，惧溺而渴死，不能如说行，多闻亦如是。<span class="_ _6"></span>”<span class="ff6"> </span></span></div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
